3. Key Design Change

Current Design

Read supplier rows from RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS
        |
        v
Sort by ATTEMPTS ASC
        |
        v
Select supplier with lowest current ATTEMPTS
        |
        v
Update selected supplier ATTEMPTS = ATTEMPTS + 1
        |
        v
Continue phone verification flow

Proposed Design

Read supplier rows from RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS
        |
        v
Filter eligible suppliers where TOTAL_ATTEMPTS > 0
        |
        v
Use TOTAL_ATTEMPTS as supplier weight
        |
        v
Generate random number within total weight
        |
        v
Select supplier based on weighted range
        |
        v
Continue phone verification flow

No runtime update will be performed on RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS.ATTEMPTS.

