10. Proposed Helper Method

A new helper method or utility class can be introduced to keep the selection logic isolated and testable.

Example class:

WeightedSupplierSelector

Responsibilities:

- Accept list of configured suppliers
- Filter suppliers where TOTAL_ATTEMPTS > 0
- Remove excluded suppliers if applicable
- Calculate total configured weight
- Generate random number using ThreadLocalRandom
- Select supplier based on cumulative weighted range
- Return selected supplier configuration

