17. Proposed Design Summary

The proposed design changes supplier selection from a stateful counter-based model to a stateless weighted-selection model.

The database remains the source for configured supplier allocation percentages through RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS.TOTAL_ATTEMPTS.

The application performs supplier selection using the configured weights and no longer updates RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS.ATTEMPTS during runtime.

This design removes the current database contention point while preserving configurable supplier allocation behavior.
